<title>USA: Damen Financial to buyback common shrs.</title>
<headline>Damen Financial to buyback common shrs.</headline>
<dateline>SCHAUMBURG, Ill. 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Damen Financial Corp said Tuesday that as the reuslt of its modified Dutch auction tender offer it will purchase 523,400 of its shares at $14.75 a share.</p>
<p>The value of the shares to be repurchased is about $7.7 million and the shares represent about 14 percent of the company's outstanding shares. The transaction is expected to close Thursday.</p>
<p>Damen Financial shares rose 3/8 to 14-3/4 Tuesday.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
